snippet.title: Freeman: Guerrilla Warfare trailer
snippet.description:
Buy the game on Steam NOW: http://store.steampowered.com/app/773951/Freeman_Guerrilla_Warfare/

Freeman: Guerrilla Warfare is set in a chaos world occupied by battling factions, bandits and warlords who seek to rule the world.

Website: https://www.freeman-game.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/playfreeman
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Play_Freeman
